works.description:
A photo that we own the copyright to, of 

our custom engagement ring.  I am amazed at how many of these "blogs"  
continue to use our photos without our authorization, and how you keep  
finding them.  The sheer number of these requests that I have had to make 

is very time consuming.  And it's somewhat disappointing that these
"blogs"  
continue to show up high in the image results using our photos of our  
engagement rings, but we do not.
